1.Setup
Open the source editor in mellon and make your first hello world


2.Make a hello world

Type in "WriteLine{"Hello World!"} "

next add a comment type ";This is made by me! "

and compile it by pressing f1 or clicking the debug icon

3.Change the title

Type in "Window.title = {"Hello world program"}"

4.Create a file a text file and delete it
Type in "Import Mellon.Filesystem"
next type "Reserve Mellon.Filesystem.createfile AS CreateFile "
next type "CreateFile(hello.text)"
next type "Mellon.filesystem.Editfile(hello.text,Hello World!)"
to delete it type "Mellon.Filesystem.Deletefile(hello.text)"
